# Frontend Visualization Patterns

## Tables Are Forbidden Except For

- **Rent roll** — unit-by-unit line items with many columns (unit, status, tenant, rent, market, gap, lease end)
- **Lease lists** — individual lease records (tenant, property, unit, rent, expiry, days left)
- **Maintenance work orders** — line-item operational records
- **Documents list** — uploaded file records

**Everything else uses visual components.** No exceptions.

## What to Use Instead

| Context | Use |
|---|---|
| Manager list | `ManagerHealthCard` grid or master-detail ranked list |
| Property list | `PropertyHealthCard` grid or master-detail ranked list |
| Portfolio summary | `StatHero`, `HealthRing`, `PipelineStrip`, `TimelineBuckets` |
| Occupancy | `HealthRing` (SVG donut) — never a `<table>` or a text percentage alone |
| Collections status | `PipelineStrip` |
| Lease timeline | `TimelineBuckets` |
| Alerts / signals | `AlertFeed` |
| Trends over time | Recharts `AreaChart` or `BarChart` |

## Primitive Library (use these, don't inline)

```
src/components/ui/
  HealthRing.tsx       — occupancy/rate donut chart
  PipelineStrip.tsx    — sequential stage visualization
  TimelineBuckets.tsx  — time-bucketed bar viz
  StatHero.tsx         — prominent metric with supporting stats
  AlertFeed.tsx        — actionable signal list
  ManagerHealthCard.tsx
  PropertyHealthCard.tsx
```

## Layout Patterns

- **List views** (`/managers`, `/properties`): master-detail split — left panel is the list, right panel is the selected entity detail. Never a full-page navigation just to see a detail.
- **Empty states**: show the structural skeleton, not an error or "no data" message. The framework is always visible.
- **Search/filter**: narrows the population of the framework, does not hide the layout.

## ❌ Banned Patterns

```tsx
// Never for entity lists or overviews
<table>
  <tr><td>Manager Name</td><td>Occupancy</td><td>Revenue</td></tr>
</table>

// Never for occupancy
<span>{pct(occupancy_rate)}</span>

// Never for portfolio summary
<div>Revenue: $45,000</div>
```

## ✅ Required Patterns

```tsx
// Entity overview
<ManagerHealthCard manager={m} />

// Occupancy — always visual
<HealthRing rate={metrics.occupancy_rate} size={56} />

// Pipeline status
<PipelineStrip stages={stages} title="Collections" />
```
